//encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS0QuBJKJ37HsqwNejcmXAHiCUx7tJdiIKHUw";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:360;s:6:"height";i:480;s:6:"source";s:48:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/79587118393763727/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:53:{i:0;s:22:"What is a chair class.";i:1;s:150:"Zumba Gold chair class is suitable for people who have mobility or balance problems or who might just want to start in a chair or when space is tight.";i:2;s:90:"Please dont confuse it with the very high impact Zumba Sentao which is where the chair is.";i:3;s:94:"This 45-miunute seated class combines muscle toning moves to give you an overall energy boost.";i:4;s:240:"Chair Zumba incorporates movements taken from Latin dances like the merengue salsa and cha cha to create an exhilarating program that aims to improve overall energy core stability muscular strength cardiovascular endurance and motor skills.";i:5;s:85:"All classes combine cardio posture correction toning weight loss flexibility and Fun.";i:6;s:210:"Zumba is a Latin American music based dancefitness programme that incorporates aerobic exercises with the dance styles of Salsa Cumbia Merengue as well as international choreographies from all around the world.";i:7;s:227:"I will be doing a LIVE 45 min Class Every Monday at 5pm Melbourne time for the month of May the 3rd 10th 17th 24th and 31st I can send you a recording of a 1 hour Zumba Gold class or 30 min Chair Zumba whenever you request one.";i:8;s:81:"It will be available to watch as many times as you like for 7days at a cost of 5.";i:9;s:80:"Please deposit it to my bank account Bank NAB Name Zoe Cordwell BSB 083-232 ACC.";i:10;s:34:"A Zumba class adapted for seniors.";i:11;s:90:"This class is all about taking care of our health in an atmosphere of celebration and joy.";i:12;s:114:"The emphasis is on cardiovascular improvement balance and muscle strength while maintaining safety for our joints.";i:13;s:51:"People who want to get some serious core work done.";i:14;s:42:"Pull up a chair and tone your entire body.";i:15;s:119:"Zumba Sentao combines strength and resistance training with innovative dance moves using a chair as your dance partner.";i:16;s:145:"A high intensity workout that focuses on defining your muscles improving overall cardiovascular health and burning major calories in the process.";i:17;s:187:"Great for active older adults looking for a modified Zumba class at a lower intensity that introduces easy-to-follow choreography with a focus on balance range of motion and coordination.";i:18;s:58:"Basic Zumba steps a little strength training a LOT of fun.";i:19;s:33:"45 minute class Zumba Gold Chair.";i:20;s:36:"A class is done entirely in a chair.";i:21;s:191:"Disability Horizons deputy editor Shannon Kelly who uses a wheelchair used a recent Zumba class to start breaking down barriers to fitness and make exercise more inclusive to disabled people.";i:22;s:42:"Pull up a chair and tone your entire body.";i:23;s:119:"Zumba Sentao combines strength and resistance training with innovative dance moves using a chair as your dance partner.";i:24;s:103:"A high intensity workout that focuses on defining your muscles improving overall cardiovascular health.";i:25;s:249:"Zumba and Chair Zumba I will be doing a LIVE 45 min Class Every Monday at 5pm Melbourne time for the month of May the 3rd 10th 17th 24th and 31st I can send you a recording of a 1 hour Zumba Gold class or 30 min Chair Zumba whenever you request one.";i:26;s:88:"To attend the regular Zumba Gold class you must check in prior to the Chair Zumba class.";i:27;s:170:"You can either attend the chair class or warm up in the Social Hall while waiting as class monitors must have both classes checked in prior to start of Zumba Chair class.";i:28;s:73:"All persons joining Zumba Club must present a Valid RCSC card with photo.";i:29;s:90:"8 Annual Membership Fee with Valid RCSC Card 4 Visitors RCSC Cardholder may try one class.";i:30;s:164:"Zumba Gold This class is perfect for active older adults who are looking for a modified Zumba class that recreates the original moves you love at a lower-intensity.";i:31;s:58:"Amanda Trollinger-Kalbach - Former Activities Coordinator.";i:32;s:107:"Having Danny Grae instruct the chair Zumba class for us at Heather Glen Senior Living is always a fun time.";i:33;s:56:"Dannys enthusiasm and energy keeps our residents moving.";i:34;s:84:"By utilizing a chair this Zumba class provides a low-impact option good for seniors.";i:35;s:103:"The class will feature seated movements that help to improve balance coordination and overall strength.";i:36;s:62:"This class occurs every Thursday from 6-7pm starting March 30.";i:37;s:354:"Chair Zumba for Seniors is a 30 minute seated gentle aerobicsphysical therapy class for seniors and other people with mobility issues taught by Zumba Instructor Evie Aronson - who has several years of experience teaching this format for blind students at Visions NYC senior citizens at Vista on 5th assisted living residence and also for Gildas Club NYC.";i:38;s:185:"Megan Pows Zumba Gold Chair class is a high-energy fun joyful and friendly fitness class for anyone who wants to exercise sitting down in a chair in a wheelchair or on a stability ball.";i:39;s:187:"It combines the party atmosphere and the loud exciting Latin and international dance moves of a high-intensity Zumba class with the specific needs of people who prefer to sit to exercise.";i:40;s:75:"Im a licensed Zumba instructor and I teach wheelchair Zumba online on Zoom.";i:41;s:79:"This class focuses on upper body movements including shoulders arms chest neck.";i:42;s:53:"Able body participants are more than welcome to join.";i:43;s:33:"Its a great workout for everyone.";i:44;s:61:"Its 8 per class and payments can be made via Venmo or PayPal.";i:45;s:62:"Class is 90 done from a chair a chair without arms works best.";i:46;s:102:"One standing Balance song and a few standing stretches included near the end of class - both optional.";i:47;s:148:"Httpswwwzumbadancemarketplacedetailsd20d23ab-ef6e-462b-87c0-e9aac65c1b6c zumba-gold-chair-with-leslie_leslie-sullins ae0tj4lnvzqmes37tm3t1261 Share.";i:48;s:125:"The design of the classes introduces easy-to-follow Zumba choreography that have been brilliantly adapted for chair exercise.";i:49;s:100:"Each class is different as it is adapted to fit the ability and range of motion of the participants.";i:50;s:36:"But the main focus is on having fun.";i:51;s:59:"No dance experience is needed and there are no wrong moves.";i:52;s:74:"Seated Zumba Gold is an excellent way to strengthen the bones and muscles.";}}